OL,3,CFormer RTE broadcaster David Davin-
OL,4,CPower dies aged 72
OL,6,FFormer broadcaster and political
OL,7,Fcorrespondent David Davin-Power has
OL,8,Fdied aged 72.
OL,10,FThe Dublin-born broadcaster began
OL,11,Fworking with RTE News in 1978, and was
OL,12,Fa presenter on RTE Radio's Morning
OL,13,FIreland programme before serving as
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland editor.
OL,16,FFormer RTE News Six One newsreader
OL,17,FBryan Dobson paid tribute to Mr Davin-
OL,18,FPower's ability to make complex
OL,19,Fstories "immediately understandable"
OL,20,Fand to hone in "on what really
OL,21,Fmattered".
