OL,6,F"More than all of that, he loved his
OL,7,Ffamily and spoke of them with huge
OL,8,Fpride and joy.
OL,10,F"When I saw him in the summer he was
OL,11,Falready very ill but was on great form
OL,12,F` wanting to talk politics: Irish, UK,
OL,13,FUS and of course RTE.
OL,15,F"Always with a glint in his eye, some
OL,16,Fmischief and his memorable laugh. We
OL,17,Fwill all miss him hugely."
