OL,6,FTaoiseach Simon Harris paid tribute to
OL,7,Fhim as "a trusted name who was
OL,8,Fwelcomed into homes across the country
OL,9,Fthroughout his long career".
OL,11,F"He was one of the first presenters of
OL,12,FMorning Ireland, an accomplished
OL,13,FNorthern Editor of RTE at a key moment
OL,14,Fin history, a political correspondent
OL,15,Fwho knew the Dail inside out, and in
OL,16,Frecent years, a witty and insightful
OL,17,Fcolumnist.
OL,19,F"David was always a consummate
OL,20,Fprofessional, a thorough journalist,
OL,21,Fand a gentleman.
OL,26,@oD@HOUqD@[O]sD@AOU{D@AOU
