OL,6,F"He was a storyteller who was generous
OL,7,Fwith his time, he was an interesting
OL,8,Fperson who was interested in other
OL,9,Fpeople, and he was kind to those
OL,10,Faround him."
OL,12,FTanaiste Micheal Martin said he was
OL,13,F"thorough and razor sharp in his
OL,14,Fquestioning and analysis, but fair".
OL,16,F"He was always driven to get to the
OL,17,Fbottom of every story he worked on. I
OL,18,Falways enjoyed my engagements with
OL,19,FDavid, and our conversations over the
OL,20,Fyears.
