OL,6,F"He had an outstanding ability to
OL,7,Fexplain even the most complicated of
OL,8,Fstories, making the news accessible to
OL,9,Fall. His contribution to journalism
OL,10,Fwas immense.
OL,12,F"My thoughts are with David's family,
OL,13,Ffriends and former colleagues at this
OL,14,Fdifficult time."
OL,16,FHe is survived by his wife Dearbhla,
OL,17,Fhis five children and his wider family.
